      "message": "IMHO, if we write it this way, the flags will become useless: some writes will forget to set them, so readers will start ignoring them to display \"correctly\" more images. That\u0027s why I would prefer if readers had to ignore extra sections if the corresponding flag is not set - that would make the flags reliable. But that\u0027s probably not a discussion for this patch?",
